SECURITY TRAINING AND AWARENESS PLAN
================================================================================
Company: Ahmnest SecureTech Solution
Effective Date: [Date]
Version: 1.0
================================================================================

1. OVERVIEW
================================================================================
This plan defines the security awareness training program for all employees
and contractors to ensure they understand their role in maintaining security.

2. TRAINING PROGRAM
================================================================================
| Training Type | Audience | Frequency | Duration |
|---------------|----------|-----------|----------|
| New Hire Security | All Employees | Upon Hire | 2 Hours |
| Phishing Awareness | All Employees | Monthly | 30 Minutes |
| Password Security | All Employees | Quarterly | 30 Minutes |
| Incident Reporting | All Employees | Quarterly | 30 Minutes |
| Data Protection | All Employees | Semi-Annually | 1 Hour |
| Advanced Security | IT Staff | Monthly | 2 Hours |

3. PHISHING SIMULATION PROGRAM
================================================================================
| Activity | Frequency | Success Criteria |
|----------|-----------|------------------|
| Simulated Phishing | Monthly | < 10% Click Rate |
| Targeted Campaigns | Quarterly | < 5% Click Rate |
| Executive Campaigns | Quarterly | < 2% Click Rate |
| Remediation Training | As Needed | 100% Completion |

4. TRAINING CONTENT
================================================================================
| Topic | Description | Delivery Method |
|-------|-------------|-----------------|
| Identifying Phishing | Spotting suspicious emails | E-learning + Simulation |
| Secure Password Practices | Creating/managing passwords | E-learning |
| Social Engineering | Recognizing manipulation | E-learning |
| Data Protection | Handling sensitive data | E-learning + Workshop |
| Incident Response | Reporting procedures | E-learning |
| Mobile Security | Securing mobile devices | E-learning |
| Home Office Security | Securing remote work | E-learning |

5. COMPLIANCE TRACKING
================================================================================
| Metric | Target | Tracking Method |
|--------|--------|-----------------|
| Training Completion Rate | 100% | LMS Tracking |
| Phishing Click Rate | < 10% | Simulation Report |
| Incident Reports | Increasing | Incident Database |
| Policy Acknowledgment | 100% | Electronic Signature |

6. RESPONSIBLE PARTIES
================================================================================
| Role | Responsibility |
|------|----------------|
| HR Director | Manage enrollment |
| IT Lead | Deliver technical training |
| CTO | Sponsor program |
| All Employees | Participate and learn |

================================================================================
